[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Creates a variable [`r] as if by [`T& r(std::forward<U>(u));]
and then initializes [*val] with [`addressof(r)].
[:zh_CN] 如同用 [`T& r(std::forward<U>(u));] 创建变量 [`r]，然后以 [`addressof(r)] 初始化 [*val]。
[div:end]
